*Reporter*: Nick Pellow
*E-mail*: [mailto:npellow@atlassian.com]

There's a mistake in the URL shown in this documentation page: 

[https://confluence.atlassian.com/jirakb/export-more-than-1000-issues-to-excel-from-issue-navigator-in-jira-cloud-779160811.html]

Currently the page shows this sample URL: 
{code:java}
https://<instance name>/sr/jira.issueviews:searchrequest-excel-all-fields/temp/SearchRequest.xls?jqlQuery=&tempMax=1000&pager/start=1001{code}
 

The correct URL is this: 
{code:java}
https://<instance name>/sr/jira.issueviews:searchrequest-excel-all-fields/temp/SearchRequest.xls?jqlQuery=&tempMax=1000&pager/start=1000{code}
Note that the final parameter should be 1000, not 1001, because it's a zero-based index.

